  Modello della BASE MOBILE di AIRA (struttura a T, profili 40x40, 2 ruote hoverboard
  motrici + 1 ruota pivotante posteriore). SCHELETRO con PLACEHOLDER: le quote qui sotto
  sono da MISURARE sul robot vero e correggere (una riga a testa, in cima).

  Frame (REP-103/105): X avanti, Y sinistra, Z su.
  - base_link = punto medio dell'ASSE delle due ruote motrici, all'altezza dell'asse.
    (E' il frame che il driver odrive_node usa per odom->base_link.)
  - base_footprint = proiezione a terra di base_link (comodo per Nav2).

  Le quote necessarie SUBITO per guidare/odometria sono solo wheel_diameter e
  wheel_separation (le stesse del driver). Il resto (T, castor) serve per la resa in
  RViz e il footprint di Nav2: si raffina piu' avanti.
--><robot name="aira_base"><!-- MISURA: carreggiata (contatti a terra) --><!-- MISURA: profilo centrale (X, va indietro) --><!-- MISURA: X del castor (negativo = dietro) --><!-- placeholder depth camera sulla testa --><!-- ============================ materiali ============================ --><material name="alu"><color rgba="0.75 0.75 0.78 1.0"/></material><material name="tyre"><color rgba="0.12 0.12 0.12 1.0"/></material><material name="caster"><color rgba="0.30 0.30 0.32 1.0"/></material><!-- ============================ base_link + footprint ============================ --><link name="base_link"/><link name="base_footprint"/><joint name="base_footprint_joint" type="fixed"><parent link="base_link"/><child link="base_footprint"/><origin rpy="0 0 0" xyz="0 0 -0.0825"/></joint><!-- ============================ profilo ANTERIORE (porta le ruote) ============================ --><link name="front_beam"><visual><geometry><box size="0.04 0.5 0.04"/></geometry><material name="alu"/></visual><collision><geometry><box size="0.04 0.5 0.04"/></geometry></collision><inertial><mass value="1.0"/><inertia ixx="0.020966666666666665" ixy="0" ixz="0" iyy="0.0002666666666666667" iyz="0" izz="0.020966666666666665"/></inertial></link><joint name="front_beam_joint" type="fixed"><parent link="base_link"/><child link="front_beam"/><origin rpy="0 0 0" xyz="0 0 0"/></joint><!-- ============================ profilo CENTRALE (va indietro) ============================ --><link name="center_beam"><visual><geometry><box size="0.6 0.04 0.04"/></geometry><material name="alu"/></visual><collision><geometry><box size="0.6 0.04 0.04"/></geometry></collision><inertial><mass value="1.0"/><inertia ixx="0.0002666666666666667" ixy="0" ixz="0" iyy="0.03013333333333333" iyz="0" izz="0.03013333333333333"/></inertial></link><joint name="center_beam_joint" type="fixed"><parent link="base_link"/><child link="center_beam"/><origin rpy="0 0 0" xyz="-0.3 0 0"/></joint><link name="left_wheel"><visual><origin rpy="1.5707963 0 0" xyz="0 0 0"/><!-- cilindro coricato lungo Y --><geometry><cylinder length="0.06" radius="0.0825"/></geometry><material name="tyre"/></visual><collision><origin rpy="1.5707963 0 0" xyz="0 0 0"/><geometry><cylinder length="0.06" radius="0.0825"/></geometry></collision><inertial><mass value="1.5"/><inertia ixx="0.0030023437499999994" ixy="0" ixz="0" iyy="0.0030023437499999994" iyz="0" izz="0.0051046875"/></inertial></link><joint name="left_wheel_joint" type="continuous"><parent link="base_link"/><child link="left_wheel"/><origin rpy="0 0 0" xyz="0 0.225 0"/><axis xyz="0 1 0"/></joint><link name="right_wheel"><visual><origin rpy="1.5707963 0 0" xyz="0 0 0"/><!-- cilindro coricato lungo Y --><geometry><cylinder length="0.06" radius="0.0825"/></geometry><material name="tyre"/></visual><collision><origin rpy="1.5707963 0 0" xyz="0 0 0"/><geometry><cylinder length="0.06" radius="0.0825"/></geometry></collision><inertial><mass value="1.5"/><inertia ixx="0.0030023437499999994" ixy="0" ixz="0" iyy="0.0030023437499999994" iyz="0" izz="0.0051046875"/></inertial></link><joint name="right_wheel_joint" type="continuous"><parent link="base_link"/><child link="right_wheel"/><origin rpy="0 0 0" xyz="0 -0.225 0"/><axis xyz="0 1 0"/></joint><!-- ============================ ruota pivotante posteriore (passiva) ============================ --><!-- Modellata come sfera: passiva, non entra nella cinematica. Il perno girevole non serve. --><link name="caster_wheel"><visual><geometry><sphere radius="0.03"/></geometry><material name="caster"/></visual><collision><geometry><sphere radius="0.03"/></geometry></collision><inertial><mass value="0.2"/><inertia ixx="7.199999999999999e-05" ixy="0" ixz="0" iyy="7.199999999999999e-05" iyz="0" izz="7.199999999999999e-05"/></inertial></link><joint name="caster_joint" type="fixed"><parent link="base_link"/><child link="caster_wheel"/><origin rpy="0 0 0" xyz="-0.55 0 -0.052500000000000005"/></joint><!-- ============================ LiDAR FHL-LD19 (placeholder mount) ============================ --><material name="lidar"><color rgba="0.10 0.10 0.12 1.0"/></material><link name="laser_link"><visual><geometry><cylinder length="0.035" radius="0.019"/></geometry><material name="lidar"/></visual><collision><geometry><cylinder length="0.035" radius="0.019"/></geometry></collision><inertial><mass value="0.05"/><inertia ixx="9.616666666666667e-06" ixy="0" ixz="0" iyy="9.616666666666667e-06" iyz="0" izz="9.024999999999999e-06"/></inertial></link><joint name="laser_joint" type="fixed"><parent link="base_link"/><child link="laser_link"/><origin rpy="0 0 0" xyz="0.1 0 0.2"/></joint><!-- ============================ CORPO: busto (pitch,tilt) + testa (pan,tilt,pitch) ============================ --><!-- Nomi giunto = canali di aira_body (/body/state): torso_pitch/tilt, head_pan/tilt/pitch.
